==How to create a gmail account:==
Go to the gmail site: https://mail.google.com

Click on create account

Insert the personal data (the phone number is required for verification)

Click on next step

Accept the conditions

Verify your identity ,and insert the number code received by sms

==How to enable gmail to send mail with onos:==

Click on "myaccount"

under the tab named
Sign-in & security	

click the "Connected apps & sites"

Find the switch "Allow less secure apps" and turn it on

Done

